{"tid":253417,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"阿諾宣佈會拍《未來戰士6》 占士金馬倫有新構思","createTime":"2017-05-22T11:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T12:30:19.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7801a4dfa80de7504bf20e979a03fe26715822c7","tid":253417,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170521/56722250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170521%2F56722250&d=aISpdGVq1OuJ%2BcpSKkhvRRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=cc2fde0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170521%2F56722250&h=5245c3b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170521/56722250</a><br />\n<br />\n第70屆康城影展現正舉行，國際影星阿諾舒華辛力加（Arnold Schwarzenegger）於當地宣傳有關環保嘅紀錄片《Wonders Of The Sea 3D 》。阿諾日前接受《Screen Daily》訪問講吓嚟緊有乜新搞作。佢透露會拍第6集《未來戰士》（The Terminator）。阿諾話最近有同占士金馬倫（James Cameron）見面，「電影將會回歸，金馬倫有啲好好嘅構思去延續電影系列。我會參演電影。」<br />\n<br />\n阿諾主演嘅《未來戰士》第五集《未來戰士：創世智能》（Terminator：Genisys）前年上映，有「龍母」艾美莉克拉克（Emilia Clarke）參演，不過當年票房成績麻麻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blacksportsonline.com/home/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/James-Cameron-Arnold-Schwarzenegger.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblacksportsonline.com%2Fhome%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FJames-Cameron-Arnold-Schwarzenegger.jpg&h=0f279482&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ecc664bc7140822aa6490a0c732cc5a9e9637bf","tid":253417,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa14b6d8bcfcf3e395d83ee2a4374b2f4bb6cf36","tid":253417,"